{"tid":1662714,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［新活動］諗到一個新的和理非活動 - 商場玩骨牌","createTime":"2019-10-19T02:47:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-19T10:14:38.000Z","uid":94771,"like":34,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"50028d8ba66ec37582253be5d869071eb54694a1","tid":1662714,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T02:47:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qeHhj3p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqeHhj3p.jpg&h=9053c0eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DxFnwbY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDxFnwbY.jpg&h=1cc913db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最重要係依個活動可以係商場到做，而且材料可以自制又容易買<br />\n<br />\n做出來有視覺效果，容易吸引眼球，而且可以用來做唔同的創作<br />\n而且推落去個下好有成功感，個骨牌做得大，真係幾好睇<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如：連猪骨牌　ＦＲＥＥ　ＨＫ骨牌　連狗骨牌<br />\n<br />\n比大家睇下Example <br />\n<br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UFGUvfJUnrQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DUFGUvfJUnrQ&d=hAhx4mZ6jCiP%2Fv5W8BSz9je9V6YwtzhhzuTx9UUfAJc%3D&h=3aea7622\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UFGUvfJUnrQ</a><br />\n[/url]<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6zpUzRmRIWE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D6zpUzRmRIWE&d=hAhx4mZ6jCiP%2Fv5W8BSz9je9V6YwtzhhzuTx9UUfAJc%3D&h=2f25f47a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6zpUzRmRIWE</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JE9yGOaF-ao\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DJE9yGOaF-ao&d=hAhx4mZ6jCiP%2Fv5W8BSz9je9V6YwtzhhzuTx9UUfAJc%3D&h=3170dbf0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JE9yGOaF-ao</a><br />\n<br />\n我覺得依個係一個唔錯的建議，大家點睇，歡迎討論<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最重要係可以拎來做文宣</span></strong>"},{"pid":"926e03eab979b43d151482b3dd86acd140ca94fc"